arcana (0.20.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bump default prune TTLs. ARCANA_AGENT_TTL default 24h -> 7d;
    ARCANA_MAILBOX_TTL default 72h -> 30d. Prune interval stays hourly.
    An idle agent that hasn't sent/received/registered in a day was
    getting evicted mid-work; the new defaults leave a week of grace
    on the listing and a month on the mailbox before either goes.
    Override via the env vars if you need shorter cleanup.

